oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Robert Cash gives birthday party, from the Nashville Times, 1940
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A captioned photo from the Nashville Times (1940), about Robert Cash’s birthday party. The caption states he was “host at a birthday party recently at the home of his parents, Mr. and Mrs. C. C. Cash, 1711 Woodland Street. Those sent at the party include: Nancy Law, Frank Bradshaw, Robert Cash, Patsy McRedmond, Reber Anne Trotman, Grandstaff Dale, Eugene Jenkins, Felix Speight?, Kelley Hill, Charles Cash, Jr., Anthony Petten, Marion Hill, Richey Stewart, Joe Trotman, Billy Craig Hayes, Betty Anne Greek, Pauline Brook, and Marianne McWilliams.” Forms part of the Nashville Times newspaper collection. 1 digital photo.
